long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Factobi Studio is AI Agents based Automation platform.
This plugin is needed in order to automate chrome with iFact or Factobi Studio, the addon does nothing without a running instance of iFact or Factobi Studio running at the same time.
The addon needs very broad permissions in order to record and replay sequences.
This addon does not collect and send any information, you can however collect information from webpages using the iFact or Factobi Studio software.
